ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[Thailand had to learn the hard way that there are no shortcuts in
obtaining the official internationally recognised status of an HPAI-free
country (6 months following the last stamped-out outbreak). The current
official announcement is in compliance with OIE's requirements, as spelled
out in OIE's Terrestrial Animal Health Code (for further details, see
update 63). - Mod.AS]
